fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network
Class IfaceLink

java.lang.Object
  fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network.IfaceLink

public class IfaceLink
extends java.lang.Object

Describes a link between an interface Iface and a network IPNet.

An IfaceLink has one IP address for the interface IPNet and one network IP address IPNet.

Author:
Patrick Lamaiziere
